@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
                                @{b}@{u}Requirements@{ub}@{uu}

@{u}Hardware@{uu}

 - Amiga Computer (Surprise :-))
 - 68000 CPU or higher
 - Modem


@{u}Software@{uu}

 - Kickstart 3.0 or higher
 - Workbench 3.0 or higher
 - Optional: reqtools.library for GUI
 - "modem".device eg. serial.device

@endnode


@NODE "Limitations" "Limitations"

                       @{b}@{u}Current Limitations!@{ub}@{uu}


At this moment, there are a few limitations to ModemActivator.

-Filename+path MAX length: 128 chars! [MAX length of tooltype!!]
-MAX devicename length: 32 chars [set by me! can be increased on request]
-MAX unit number: 999 [just to be on the safe side :-)]
-MAX program/script stack size: 32768 bytes
-May or may not work wit other devices than serial.device
-Max wait interval is 999 seconds

@EndNode
