@NODE "Bugs" "Those Nasty Bugs!"

@{b}@{u}List of known bugs in Modem Activator:@{ub}@{uu}


-MA can't detect if the program/script you have chosen is run or not, since
 I can't make SystemTagList() return the correct errorcodes. It always return
 succes, even if the program doesn't excist!
 BUT it is being worked on!


